uted%20a%20high-level%20enquiry%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20all%20the%20relevant%20aspects%20of%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20made%20allegations%20regarding%20a%20%26quot%3Bpotential%26quot%3B%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20agents%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENijjar%2C%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20banned%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20and%20one%20of%20India's%20most-wanted%20terrorists%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERefuting%20the%20allegations%20as%20%26quot%3Bpolitically%20motivated%26quot%3B%2C%20India%20said%20Canada%20should%20share%20evidence%20-%20a%20request%20Ottawa%20has%20so%20far%20declined.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happens%20in%20international%20relations%20from%20time%20to%20time%20such%20challenges%20can%20arise.%20So%2C%20we%20very%20sincerely%20have%20told%20the%20Canadians%20saying%20that%20look%20it's%20up%20to%20you%2C%20I%20mean%20your%20choice%20whether%20you%20would%20like%20us%20to%20pursue%20it%2C%20further%20look%20into%20it%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Minister%20told%20the%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20last%20month%2C%20India's%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20Canada%2C%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Verma%2C%20also%20said%20that%20Indian%20government%20is%20cooperating%20with%20an%20American%20investigation%20into%20alleged%20thwarted%20assassination%20attempt%20and%20not%20Canada's%20probe%20into%20the%20June%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20British%20Columbia's%20Surrey%20due%20to%20a%20disparity%20between%20the%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Verma%20said%20India%20was%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdecidedly%26quot%3B%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20homicide%2C%20terming%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%20and%20absurd%20allegation.%26quot%3B%20The%20allegations%20caused%