I%20they%20hope%20borrowers%20with%20hardship%20will%20be%20included%20in%20the%20final%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-what-is-next-biden-debt-cancellation-relief-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekey%20step%20toward%20crafting%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20next%20attempt%20at%20student-loan%20forgiveness%3C%2Fa%3E%20ended%20on%20a%20contentious%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20October%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20has%20been%20meeting%20with%20a%20group%20of%20negotiators%20%E2%80%94%20comprised%20of%20borrowers%2C%20legal%20experts%2C%20advocates%2C%20and%20more%20%E2%80%94%20to%20provide%20input%20on%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-long-will-take-cancel-student-debt-higher-education-act-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudent-debt%20relief%20under%20the%20Higher%20Education%20Act%20of%201965%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-supreme-court-strikes-down-debt-cancellation-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruck%20down%20Biden's%20first%20attempt%20at%20debt%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20promptly%20announced%20it%20would%20pursue%20another%20route%20under%20the%20HEA%2C%20which%20requires%20the%20administration%20to%20undergo%20a%20process%20known%20as%20negotiated%20rulemaking.%20The%20process%20is%20lengthy%2C%20and%20it%20entails%20a%20series%20of%20negotiation%20sessions%20with%20stakeholders%20to%20help%20create%20the%20draft%20text%2C%20and%20the%20public%20later%20has%20an%20opportunity%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20six%20days%20of%20sessions%20that%20began%20in%20October%2C%20negotiations%20concluded%20on%20December%2012%20%E2%80%94%20and%20members%20of%20the%20committee%20were%20not%20able%20to%20reach%20a%20consensus%20on%20all%20of%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Erelief%20provisions%20the%20department%20proposed.%20Some%20sticking%20points%20for%20the%20negotiators%20included%20the%20department's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-who-will-qualify-second-attempt-biden-education-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproposed%20cap%20of%20%2420%2C000%20on%20any%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E%20borrowers%20might%20get%2C%20along%20with%20the%20exclusion%20of%20a%20relief%20category%20for%20borrowers%20experiencing%20hardship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJessica%20Ranucci%2C%20an%20attorney%20at%20the%20New%20York%20Legal%20Assistance%20Group%20and%20a%20negotiator%20on%20the%20committee%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bthose%20limits%20were%20disappointing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20does%20make%20this%20negotiation%20much%20more%20complicated%20because%20we%20are%20working%20on%20a%20backdrop%20of%20legal%20principles%20that%20are%20unsettled%2C%26quot%3B%20Ranucci%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20decision%20in%20any%20way%20forecloses%20any%20avenue%20towards%20broader%20debt%20cancellation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20negotiators%20asked%20the%20department%20to%20add%20another%20session%20to%20further%20discuss%20relief%20for%20borrowers%20with%20hardship%2C%20the%20department%20has%20not%20yet%20commented%20on%20whether%20it%20will%20do%20so.%20A%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Biden-Harris%20Administration%20remains%20deeply%20committed%20to%20providing%20student%20loan%20relief%20for%20as%20many%20borrowers%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20day%20one%2C%20we%20have%20made%20significant%20progress%20in%20identifying%20different%20ways%20to%20deliver%20relief%20for%20more%20than%203.6%20million%20borrowers%20and%20fix%20our%20broken%20student%20loan%20system%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20identify%20more%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20thank%20the%20negotiators%20for%20their%20work%20to%20reach%20consensus%20on%20many%20key%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20will%20share%20more%20information%20on%20the%20next%20step%20in%20the%20process%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20issuance%20of%20a%20notice%20of%20proposed%20rulemaking%20and%20our%20continued%20work%20to%20deliver%20relief%20to%20borrowers%20%E2%80%94%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhere%20the%20relief%20currently%20stands%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department's%20proposals%20for%20relief%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-who-will-qualify-second-attempt-biden-education-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eup%20to%20%2420%2C000%20in%20relief%20for%20five%20groups%20of%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20on%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%20with%20balances%20greater%20than%20what%20they%20originally%20borrowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20borrowers%20with%20balances%20greater%20than%20what%20they%20originally%20borrowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20whose%20loans%20entered%20repayment%20at%20least%2020%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20eligible%20for%20relief%20under%20targeted%20loan%20forgiveness%20and%20repayment%20programs%2C%20like%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%2C%20but%20have%20not%20yet%20applied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20those%20who%20attended%20schools%20that%20left%20them%20with%20unaffordable%20debt%20compared%20to%20post-graduation%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20negotiators%20did%20not%20agree%20with%20the%20department's%20proposed%20%2420%2C000%20cap%20on%20the%20forgiveness%20%E2%80%94%20an%20amount%20the%20department's%20representative%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bmeaningful.%26quot%3B%20Wisdom%20Cole%2C%20national%20director%20of%20the%20NAACP's%20youth%20and%20college%20division%20and%20a%20negotiator%20on%20the%20committee%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%2420%2C000%20%26quot%3Bis%20the%20floor%2C%20it's%20not%20the%20ceiling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20is%20as%20expansive%20as%20possible%20because%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20whose%20debt%20is%20far%20above%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Cole%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20average%20Black%20borrower%20has%20around%20%2450%2C000%20in%20student%20debt.%20%26quot%3BThat%20%2420%2C000%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20enough%20to%20make%20that%20sufficient%20of%20a%20difference.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPromising%20signs%20for%20borrowers%20%E2%80%94%20but%20experts%20and%20lawmakers%20want%20more%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERanucci%20highlighted%20the%20group%20of%20borrowers%20who%20attended%20low-value%20schools%20that%20left%20them%20with%20too%20much%20debt%20compared%20to%20earnings%2C%20particularly%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanceling-student-debt-defrauded-borrowers-not-enough-top-executives-liable-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschools%20that%20displayed%20misconduct%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20led%20the%20Education%20Department%20to%20cut%20off%20the%20flow%20of%20federal%20financial%20aid.%20She%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Btremendous%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20committee%20reached%20consensus%20on%20giving%20those%20borrowers%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20regulation%20really%20is%20super%20important%20in%20that%20it%20bridges%20the%20gap%20between%20students%20who%20need%20relief%20when%20their%20school%20ends%20participation%20in%20the%20federal%20financial%20aid%20program%20and%20students%20who%20are%20already%20entitled%20to%20get%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Ranucci%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20disadvantaged%20borrowers%20because%20by%20definition%2C%20they%20go%20to%20the%20programs%20that%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20has%20decided%20are%20no%20longer%20entitled%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20federal%20financial%20aid%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20many%20of%20the%20negotiators%20%E2%80%94%20and%20some%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20%E2%80%94%20want%20the%20Education%20Department%20to%20consider%20relief%20for%20even%20more%20borrowers%20as%20it%20moves%20forward%20in%20the%20process.%20A%20group%20of%20Democrats%20including%20Sen.%20Elizabeth%20Warren%20and%20Rep.%20Ayanna%20Pressley%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20Education%20Secretary%20Miguel%20Cardona%20on%20December%2011%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-getting-student-loan-forgiveness-democrats-want-more-relief-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eurging%20him%20to%20consider%20broader%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20including%20removing%20the%20%2420%2C000%20cap%20for%20borrowers%20whose%20balance%20exceeds%20the%20principal%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20more%20must%20be%20done%20to%20improve%20the%20draft%20regulatory%20text%20to%20meet%20President%20Biden's%20objective%20of%20'provid%5Bing%5D%20student%20debt%20relief%20to%20as%20many%20borrowers%20as%20possible%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%2C'%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECole%20said%20he%20hopes%20the%20department%20will%20truly%20take%20more%20expansive%20relief%20into%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHardship%20is%20an%20area%20we%20were%20really%20looking%20forward%20to%2C%20to%20leaning%20in%20on%2C%20and%20discussing%20the%20various%20hardships%20that%20Black%20borrowers%20go%20through%20in%20even%20struggling%20to%20pay%20back%20their%20student%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20Cole%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20I%20think%20that%20if%20we%20want%20to%20get%20this%20right%2C%20we%20have%20to%20recognize%20that%20having%20debt%20in%20itself%20is%20the%20hardship.%20If%20you%20are%20having%20to%20take%20on%20student%20debt%2C%20that%20is%20the%20hardship%2C%20point%20blank%2C%20period.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-student-loan-borrowers-will-get-debt-cancellation-biden-hardship-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702810981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b451f50edbc52a8644d81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-student-loan-borrowers-will-get-debt-cancellation-biden-hardship-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Experts%20who%20worked%20with%20the%20Education%20Department%20on%20its%20new%20student-loan%20forgiveness%20plan%20expressed%20frustration%20at%20the%20small%20scale%20of%20proposed%20relief.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-student-loan-borrowers-will-get-debt-cancellation-biden-hardship-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%20To%20NDTV%20On%20How%20She%20Balanced%20Law%20Career%2C%20Family%20Life%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMore%20women%20are%20coming%20forward%20to%20take%20up%20roles%20in%20the%20country's%20judiciary%2C%20once%20a%20male-dominated%20space%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Nagarathna%2C%2061%2C%20is%20in%20line%20to%20be%20the%20country's%20first%20woman%20Chief%20Justice.%20This%20morning%2C%20she%20attended%20a%20lecture%20at%20National%20Law%20School%20of%20India%20University%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20in%20the%20memory%20of%20her%20father%20and%20India's%2019th%20Chief%20Justice%20ES%20Venkataramaiah.%20The%20memorial%20lecture%20was%20delivered%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20said%20that%20while%20she%20was%20determined%20to%20continue%20a%20career%20in%20the%20judiciary%2C%20she%20did%20not%20know%20she%20would%20become%20a%20judge%20and%20get%20elevated%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20%26quot%3BAs%20the%20years%20rolled%20by%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20and%20dreams%20were%20fulfilled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20her%20father's%20advice%20to%20her%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20her%20judicial%20career%2C%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20would%20always%20tell%20me%20to%20complete%20work%20in%20time%20and%20not%20procrastinate.%20As%20they%20say%2C%20finish%20tomorrow's%20tasks%20today%20and%20today's%20tasks%20now%20because%20you%20never%20know%20when%20somebody%20will%20knock%20on%20the%20door%20and%20you%20have%20to%20serve%20them.%20Another%20advice%20was%20to%20always%20be%20present%20in%20court%20when%20cases%20come%20up.%20Absence%20of%20an%20advocate%20in%20court%20will%20prejudice%20the%20case.%20These%20are%20two%20pieces%20of%20advice%20he%20gave%20me.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20profession%20in%20the%20country%2C%20she%20said%2C%20was%20male-dominated.%20%26quot%3BFor%20women%20to%20continue%20in%20the%20profession%2C%20especially%20when%20they%20get%20married%20and%20have%20children%20is%20difficult%20unless%20they%20have%20support%20from%20the%20family.%20Therefore%2C%20unless%20there%20is%20cooperation%20from%20seniors%2C%20the%20system%20and%20the%20family%2C%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20for%20women%20to%20continue%20their%20practice.%20As%20I%20always%20say%2C%20many%20women%20get%20into%20the%20profession%20but%20many%20do%20not%20reach%20the%20higher%20echelons.%20It%20is%20because%20of%20the%20onerous%20responsibilities%20of%20women%20in%20the%20profession%20as%20well%20as%20the%20family%20that%20may%20deter%20them%20from%20continuing%20after%20a%20point%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20decision%20that%20has%20to%20be%20made%20by%20the%20woman%20by%20bringing%20together%20her%20family%20and%20the%20system%20and%20balancing%20the%20two%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Nagaratha%20said%20things%20are%20changing%20now.%20%26quot%3BMany%20women%20are%20now%20crossing%20hurdles%20and%20coming%20forward.%20Now%2C%20at%20the%20district%20judiciary%20level%2C%20over%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20judges%20are%20women.%20There%20are%20many%20women%20now%20in%20legal%20practice%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20how%20she%20managed%20to%20strike%20the%20balance%20between%20work%20and%20family%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20lucky%20on%20that%20front.%20My%20husband%2C%20BN%20Gopalakrishna%2C%20has%20always%20given%20prominence%20to%20my%20work%20and%20taken%20much%20of%20the%20domestic%20responsibilities%20on%20his%20shoulder.%20My%20daughters%20Nayanthara%20and%20Prerana%2C%20understood%20very%20early%20that%20they%20have%20a%20working%20mother.%20They%20knew%20they%20could%20not%20disturb%20their%20mother%20and%20they%20grew%20up%20on%20their%20own.%20That%20lessened%20my%20guilt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happens%20with%20a%20woman%20is%20that%20as%20and%20when%20she%20achieves%20success%2C%20there%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20guilt%20because%20she%20feels%20she%20might%20have%20neglected%20her%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20saying%20that%20behind%20every%20successful%20man%2C%20there%20is%20a%20woman.%20But%20I%20would%20say%20that%20behind%20every%20successful%20woman%2C%20there%20is%20a%20family.%20So%20I%20am%20very%20lucky%20that%20my%20family%20supported%20me%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20what%20would%20be%20her%20advice%20to%20young%20women%20eager%20to%20build%20a%20career%20in%20law%2C%20the%20judge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMore%20women%20should%20come%20into%20the%20profession%20and%20decide%20how%20to%20divide%20time%20between%20work%20and%20family.%20They%20need%20to%20be%20determined%20that%20husband%2C%20children%20and%20in-laws%20(need%20attention)%2C%20but%20work%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%26quot%3B%C2%A0She%20said%20if%20women%20advocates%20receive%20support%20from%20their%20families%2C%20there%20will%20be%20more%20women%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702810680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fmcmqrd4g_justice-nagarathna-exclusive_625x300_17_December_23.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjustice-bv-nagarathna-to-ndtv-on-how-she-balanced-law-career-family-life-4690757%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20women%20are%20coming%20forward%20to%20take%20up%20roles%20in%20the%20country's%20judiciary%2C%20once%20a%20male-dominated%20space%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjustice-bv-nagarathna-to-ndtv-on-how-she-balanced-law-career-family-life-4690757%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjustice-bv-nagarathna-to-ndtv-on-how-she-balanced-law-career-family-life-4690757%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjustice-bv-nagarathna-to-ndtv-on-how-she-balanced-law-career-family-life-4690757%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%2010%20products%20that%20have%20shrunk%20the%20most%20under%20shrinkflation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20French%20supermarket%20chain%20Carrefour%20has%20put%20labels%20on%20its%20shelves%20this%20week%20warning%20shoppers%20of%20''shrinkflation''%2C%20the%20phenomenon%20where%20manufacturers%20reduce%20pack%20sizes%20rather%20than%20increase%20prices%2C%20at%20Carrefour%20hypermarket%20in%20Premery%20on%20September%2019%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b22707a3c8094d5dcef65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223392%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20French%20supermarket%20chain%20Carrefour%20has%20put%20labels%20on%20its%20shelves%20this%20week%20warning%20shoppers%20of%20''shrinkflation''%2C%20the%20phenomenon%20where%20manufacturers%20reduce%20pack%20sizes%20rather%20than%20increase%20prices%2C%20at%20Carrefour%20hypermarket%20in%20Premery%20on%20September%2019%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EMehdi%20Taamallah%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20you%20feel%20like%20you've%20been%20going%20through%20paper%20towels%20and%20toilet%20paper%20more%20quickly%2C%20you're%20right.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHousehold%20paper%20products%20are%20victims%20of%20shrinkflation%2C%20where%20goods%20get%20smaller%20but%20stay%20the%20same%20price.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20report%20looked%20at%20which%20products%20have%20shrunk%20the%20most%20as%20inflation%20rose.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20your%20imagination%3A%20Things%20are%20getting%20smaller%2C%20and%20more%20expensive.%20It's%20been%20termed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshrinkflation-grocery-stores-pringles-cereal-candy-bars-chocolate-toilet-paper-cadbury-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eshrinkflation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Brands%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrocery-consumers-goods-are-getting-smaller-with-shrinkflation-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eshrinking%20the%20size%20of%20their%20goods%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20keeping%20prices%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20strategy%20that's%20meant%20in%20part%20to%20hide%20price%20hikes%3B%20a%20more%20expensive%20product%20might%20turn%20shoppers%20off%2C%20but%20a%20chip%20package%20with%20a%20handful%20fewer%20chips%2C%20and%20the%20same%20price%2C%20is%20a%20sneakier%20way%20of%20giving%20consumers%20less%20for%20their%20buck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20who%20are%20the%20main%20culprits%20of%20shrinkflation%3F%20Senator%20Bob%20Casey%2C%20a%20Democrat%20from%20Pennsylvania%2C%20asked%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%20for%20its%20data%20on%20which%20products%20have%20been%20impacted%20the%20most%20by%20shrinkflation.%20Casey's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.casey.senate.gov%2Fnews%2Freleases%2Fless-bang-for-your-buck-casey-releases-shrinkflation-report-exposing-big-corporations-for-reducing-product-size-while-keeping-prices-high%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20reveals%20that%20several%20common%20household%20items%20have%20indeed%20been%20shrinking%3B%20your%20breakfast%20has%20perhaps%20been%20particularly%20impacted%2C%20with%20coffee%20and%20fresh%20pastries%20getting%20smaller%20and%20pricier.%20And%20if%20you%20feel%20like%20you're%20going%20through%20paper%20towels%20and%20toilet%20paper%20at%20a%20rapid%20clip%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20your%20imagination%3A%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20your%20household%20paper%20products%20%E2%80%94%20things%20like%20paper%20towels%20and%20toilet%20paper%20%E2%80%94%20are%20seeing%20the%20largest%20price%20increases%20from%20shrinkflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F6qUzj%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Items%20with%20the%20most%20shrinkflation%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EShrinkflation%20is%20one%20way%20that%20policymakers%20and%20advocates%20say%20companies%20are%20attempting%20to%20squeeze%20more%20profits%20out%20of%20their%20customers.%20As%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%20%E2%80%94%20who%20calls%20the%20practice%20%26quot%3Bdownsizing%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Fopub%2Fbtn%2Fvolume-12%2Fmeasuring-shrinkflation-and-its-impact-on-inflation.htm%23_edn1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edocuments%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20a%20tactic%20that%20makes%20sense%20if%20firms%20want%20to%20hike%20prices.%20Buyers%20are%20much%20more%20sensitive%20to%20seeing%20a%20price%20that's%20higher%20than%20a%20package%20that's%20a%20little%20smaller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCorporations%20are%20only%20getting%20more%20creative%20as%20they%20rake%20in%20record%20profits%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Pennsylvania%20families%3A%20shrinking%20the%20size%20of%20their%20products%20while%20keeping%20the%20same%20sticker%20price.%20This%20corporate%20greed%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20that%20Americans%20are%20frustrated%20by%20expensive%20grocery%20bills%2C%26quot%3B%20Senator%20Casey%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI.%20%26quot%3BMy%20new%20report%20not%20only%20exposes%20them%20for%20their%20greed%20but%20outlines%20the%20steps%20we%20need%20to%20take%20to%20combat%20it%20and%20put%20more%20money%20back%20into%20the%20pockets%20of%20working%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShrinkflation%20isn't%20a%20new%20practice%2C%20as%20a%20report%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20St.%20Louis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fresearch.stlouisfed.org%2Fpublications%2Fpage1-econ%2F2022%2F12%2F01%2Fbeyond-inflation-numbers-shrinkflation-and-skimpflation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edocuments%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Ice%20cream%20containers%20have%20been%20shrinking%20for%20years%2C%20from%2064-ounce%20containers%20to%2048-ounce%20containers%20beginning%20in%202008%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fworklife%2Farticle%2F20180510-the-food-you-buy-really-is-shrinking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eper%20the%20BBC%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Same%20with%20cans%20of%20coffee%2C%20which%20shrunk%20from%20one%20pound%20of%20coffee%20to%2013%20ounces%20in%20the%201980's%2C%20and%20then%20contracting%20even%20further%20to%2011%20ounces%20by%202003%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fa-pound-of-coffee-07-03-2003%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECBS%20News%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%2C%20as%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20research%20notes%2C%20it's%20legal%20for%20businesses%20to%20shrink%20their%20products%20%E2%80%94%20they%20just%20need%20to%20accurately%20list%20the%20quantity%20of%20what's%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20if%20you're%20at%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20or%20a%20drug%20store%2C%20you%20may%20not%20know%20that%20your%20favorite%20toilet%20paper%20roll%20used%20to%20have%20264%20sheets%2C%20but%20now%20has%20244.%20That's%20where%20Casey%20wants%20to%20see%20some%20direct%20action%3A%20He's%20asking%20major%20food%20and%20beverage%20trade%20associations%20how%20their%20members%20came%20upon%20their%20new%20pricing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20if%20they've%20notified%20customers%20about%20how%20their%20product%20sizes%20have%20changed.%20In%20France%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20a%20supermarket%20has%20stuck%20warnings%20on%20it%20shelves%20about%20products%20that%20have%20been%20shrinkflated%2C%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-66809188%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20kinds%20of%20changes%20are%20often%20intended%20to%20obscure%20the%20very%20real%20fact%20that%20American%20families%20are%20getting%20less%20for%20their%20money.%20It%20is%20obvious%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20toilet%20paper%20rose%3B%20it%20is%20harder%20to%20detect%20that%20rolls%20shrank%20in%20size%2C%26quot%3B%20Casey%20writes%20in%20his%20report.%20%26quot%3BBut%20both%20have%20the%20same%20effect%3A%20American%20families%20are%20getting%20less%20and%20corporations%20are%20making%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-groceries-toilet-paper-shrinkflation-smaller-packages-same-price-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702810621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b22907a3c8094d5dcef7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-groceries-toilet-paper-shrinkflation-smaller-packages-same-price-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yes%2C%20you%20are%20going%20through%20toilet%20paper%20quicker.%20%26quot%3BShrinkflation%26quot%3B%20is%20hitting%20these%20items%20the%20most.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-groceries-toilet-paper-shrinkflation-smaller-packages-same-price-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lebanon%20rescues%2051%20people%20from%20sinking%20migrant%20boat%3A%20Army%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702810591000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106064388%2Cimgsize-51634.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Flebanon-rescues-51-people-from-sinking-migrant-boat-army%2Farticleshow%2F106064033.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106064033.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ELebanon%20rescues%20over%2050%20people%2C%20mostly%20Syrians%2C%20from%20sinking%20migrant%20boat%20off%20Tripoli%20coast.%20Boat%20was%20used%20for%20illegal%20people%20smuggling.%20Migrants%20leaving%20Leb