ntimicrobial%2C%20reusable%20pee%20cloth.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657bcdd050edbc52a864968f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Kula%20cloth%2C%20which%20is%20an%20antimicrobial%2C%20reusable%20pee%20cloth.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGarrett%20said%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkulacloth.com%2Fcollections%2Fstock-prints%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKula%20cloth%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20a%20game%20changer%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20using%20the%20restroom%20with%20van%20life.%20The%20%2420%20item%20is%20an%20antimicrobial%2C%20reusable%20pee%20cloth%20that's%20easy%20to%20carry%20on%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20frequent%20hiker%20and%20backpacker%2C%20and%20I've%20had%20my%20eye%20on%20a%20Kula%20cloth%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20And%20since%20my%20van%20wasn't%20going%20to%20have%20a%20bathroom%2C%20Garrett%20said%20it%20was%20the%20ideal%20time%20to%20buy%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20just%20makes%20your%20life%20easier%20because%20you%20could%20stop%20and%20pee%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20road%20at%20any%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20a%20pee%20cloth%20would%20mean%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20to%20worry%20for%20two%20weeks%20about%20throwing%20away%20used%20toilet%20paper%2C%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bit's%20literally%20the%20best%20thing%20in%20the%20whole%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20people%20encouraged%20me%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20weather.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Business%20Insider's%20author%20wears%20warm%20clothes%20outside%20her%20van.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657bd2657a3c8094d5dd5a83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20author%20wears%20warm%20clothes%20outside%20her%20van.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20people%20said%20that%20traveling%20in%20a%20van%20would%20mean%20needing%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20understand%20whatever%20is%20going%20on%20outside%20will%20probably%20affect%20you%20on%20the%20inside%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwhereis_brittany%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBrittany%20Newson%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20living%20in%20a%20travel%20trailer%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20it's%20rain%2C%20snow%2C%20or%20heat%2C%20everyone%20agreed%20I%20should%20pack%20with%20that%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40sierra.fernald%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESierra%20Fernald%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2023%2C%20said%20I%20shouldn't%20only%20consider%20the%20weather%2C%20but%20how%20I%20handle%20it.%20Fernald%20said%20she%20hates%20the%20cold%20and%20there%20were%20times%20in%20her%20Ram%20ProMaster%20van%20when%20it%20felt%20impossible%20to%20get%20out%20of%20her%20warm%20bed%20in%20the%20morning.%20So%20she%20invested%20in%20warmer%20clothes%20and%20a%20heater%20to%20make%20those%20chilly%20mornings%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefinitely%20prepare%20for%20the%20weather%2C%20and%20maybe%20over-prepare%20a%20little%20bit%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20while%20it%20might%20be%20tempting%20to%20overpack%2C%20multiple%20people%20encouraged%20me%20to%20keep%20things%20light.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sprinter%20van%20Insider's%20author%20rented%20for%20two%20weeks%20from%20Native%20Campervans.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655c46574ca513d8242caa87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20van%20all%20packed%20up.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20people%20said%20I%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20live%20and%20travel%20in%20a%20crowded%20van%2C%20so%20they%20encouraged%20me%20to%20evaluate%20if%20and%20how%20I%20was%20going%20to%20use%20every%20item%20I%20packed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCome%20in%20with%20the%20bare%20minimums%20and%20see%20how%20you%20like%20to%20live%20in%20the%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Newson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThen%20you%20will%20see%20what%20it%20is%20that%20you%20would%20need%20in%20order%20to%20be%20happy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorst-case%20scenario%2C%20I%20could%20always%20stop%20at%20a%20store%20along%20the%20way%20to%20pick%20up%20anything%20I'd%20forgotten.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETheir%20tips%20worked%2C%20and%20I%20embarked%20on%20my%20two-week%20trip%20without%20leaving%20anything%20major%20behind.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Business%20Insider's%20author%20in%20her%20rental%20van.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657c8bc350edbc52a864cf29%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20author%20in%20her%20rental%20van.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20did%20overpack%2C%20the%20people%20I%20spoke%20with%20shared%20helpful%20suggestions%20that%20made%20a%20drastic%20difference%20throughout%20my%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20grabbing%20a%20first-aid%20kit%20and%20portable%20jump%20starter%20gave%20me%20confidence%20and%20reassurance%20throughout%20the%20two%20weeks.%20And%20not%20worrying%20about%20used%20toilet%20paper%20thanks%20to%20Garrett's%20Kula%20cloth%20suggestion%20was%20a%20major%20luxury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'd%20add%20a%20few%20more%20items%20to%20my%20packing%20list%20for%20a