st-for-riteish-deshmukh-says-the-greatest-man-is-all-mine%2Farticleshow%2F106062839.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106062839.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EGenelia%20D'Souza%20shares%20a%20delightful%20black%20and%20white%20photo%20of%20her%20and%20husband%20Ritesh%20Deshmukh%20on%20his%20birthday%2C%20expressing%20her%20admiration%20for%20him.%20The%20couple%20is%20known%20for%20their%20adorable%20chemistry%20and%20mutual%20support%2C%20collaborating%20on%20several%20film%20projects.%20Genelia%20took%20a%20break%20from%20showbiz%20to%20prioritize%20her%20marriage%2C%20not%20because%20Ritesh%20asked%20her%20to%2C%20but%20because%20she%20wanted%20to.%20They%20have%20consistently%20set%20relationship%20goals%20and%20have%20been%20each%20other's%20biggest%20cheerleaders.%20The%20actress%20has%20a%20few%20projects%20in%20the%20timeline.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20paid%20%2420%20for%20a%20ticket%20to%20IKEA's%20all-you-can-eat%20annual%20Swedish%20Christmas%20feast%20%E2%80%94%20here's%20what%20it%20was%20like%20to%20attend%20'Julbord'%20in%20NYC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657ca80b7a3c8094d5dda7b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIKEA%20hosts%20an%20annual%20Swedish%20Christmas%20feast%20called%20Julbord%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIKEA%20stores%20host%20an%20annual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fchristmas-eve-traditions-around-the-world-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESwedish%20Christmas%20feast%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20restaurants%20called%20%26quot%3BJulbord.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20feast%20is%20served%20buffet%20style%20and%20includes%20a%20huge%20spread%20of%20traditional%20Swedish%20Christmas%20dishes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETickets%20for%20the%20event%20cost%20%2420%20for%20adults%20and%20%2410%20for%20children%20through%20IKEA's%20free%20loyalty%20program.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIKEA%20is%20best%20known%20for%20its%20wide%20array%20of%20furniture%20and%20home%20goods%2C%20but%20its%20ever-famous%20meatballs%20have%20to%20be%20a%20close%20second%20%E2%80%94%20lingonberry%20jam%20optional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20meatballs%20are%20delicious%20all%20year%20round%2C%20they're%20also%20a%20popular%20holiday%20dish.%20As%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20IKEA%20actually%20hosts%20an%20entire%20Swedish%20Christmas%20feast%20each%20year%20at%20every%20one%20of%20its%20stores%2C%20and%20the%20meatballs%20are%20only%20a%20small%20part%20of%20the%20festivities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feast%20is%20called%20Julbord%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20%26quot%3BChristmas%20table%26quot%3B%20in%20English%2C%20and%20consists%20of%20multiple%20courses%20of%20traditional%20Swedish%20specialties.%20IKEA%2C%20a%20Swedish%20company%2C%20has%20been%20running%20Julbord%20celebrations%20in%20its%20stores%20since%202009%2C%20a%20company%20representative%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20IKEA's%20Julbord%20feast%20is%20served%20as%20an%20all-you-can-eat%20buffet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20went%20to%20IKEA%20for%20the%20very%20first%20time%20(I'm%20not%20sure%20how%20that's%20possible%20either%2C%20don't%20worry)%2C%20and%20through%20pure%20serendipity%20I%20happened%20to%20go%20on%20the%20very%20day%20my%20local%20IKEA%20in%20Brooklyn%20was%20hosting%20its%20annual%20Julbord%20%E2%80%94%20so%20of%20course%20I%20had%20to%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20it%20was%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFirst%20I%20had%20to%20get%20to%20IKEA.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b777950edbc52a864776a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20went%20to%20the%20IKEA%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20NYC.%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IKEA%20closest%20to%20my%20Manhattan%20apartment%20is%20in%20the%20Red%20Hook%20Neighborhood%20of%20Brooklyn.%20The%20trip%20took%20about%20an%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20two%20subway%20lines%2C%20then%20a%2030-minute%20walk.%20There's%20a%20free%20IKEA%20ferry%20that%20goes%20from%20Manhattan%20straight%20to%20the%20IKEA%20storefront%2C%20but%20it%20only%20runs%20on%20the%20weekend.%20I%20went%20on%20a%20Friday%20afternoon%20(and%20somehow%20convinced%20both%20my%20boyfriend%20and%20roommate%20to%20come%20with%20me).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20went%20straight%20to%20the%20food%20court.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222730%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b77ff0ec98e92f74fb2dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20restaurant%20was%20closed%20when%20I%20got%20there%20around%202%3A30.%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restaurant%20was%20closed%20%E2%80%94%20an%20upsetting%20turn%20of%20events.%20Then%20I%20saw%20the%20sign%20about%20Julbord%2C%20and%20everything%20was%20okay%20again.%20IKEA%20says%20on%20its%20website%20that%20Julbord%20tickets%20must%20be%20bought%20in%20advance%2C%20but%20after%20asking%20around%2C%20an%20IKEA%20employee%20said%20we%20could%20buy%20tickets%20right%20there%20and%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETickets%20cost%20%2420%20per%20person.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b78707a3c8094d5dd3897%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222459%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETickets%20cost%20about%20%2420%20per%20person.%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20members%20of%20the%20IKEA%20Family%20loyalty%20program%2C%20which%20is%20free%20to%20sign%20up%20for%2C%20tickets%20cost%20%2419.99%20for%20adults%20and%20%249.99%20for%20kids%2012%20and%20under.%20For%20non-members%2C%20they%20cost%20%2424.99%20and%20%2412.99%20respectively.%20Naturally%2C%20my%20first%20course%20of%20action%20was%20to%20become%20part%20of%20the%20IKEA%20Family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20was%20quite%20the%20line%20to%20get%20in.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223019%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b78d050edbc52a8647802%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222706%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20were%20many%20people%20waiting.%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Brooklyn%20IKEA%20offered%20two%20Julbord%20seatings%3A%20one%20from%203-5%20p.m.%20and%20another%20from%206-8%20p.m.%20IKEA%20later%20told%20me%20that%20each%20seating%20at%20the%20location%20could%20accommodate%20around%20200%20people%2C%20and%20both%20were%20nearly%20sold%20out.%20I%20felt%20lucky%20that%20we%20were%20able%20to%20get%20tickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20entered%20the%20cafeteria%20and%20handed%20over%20our%20tickets%2C%20an%20employee%20gave%20us%20a%20chance%20to%20write%20our%20names%20on%20the%20backs%20to%20enter%20a%20raffle.%20The%20prize%20was%20an%20advent%20calendar%2C%20a%20bottle%20of%20Vintersaga%2C%20and%20a%20tin%20of%20cookies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20restaurant's%20cafeteria%20was%20decked%20out%20in%20festive%20decorations.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b79147a3c8094d5dd38dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20restaurant%20had%20festive%20decorations.%3Cp%3EIKEA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20star-shaped%20lanterns%2C%20which%20I%20later%20saw%20for%20sale%2C%20as%20well%20as%20evergreens.%20Christmas%20music%20played%20over%20the%20speakers%2C%20but%20there%20was%20also%20someone%20playing%20live%20music%20on%20a%20keyboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20claiming%20a%20table%2C%20I%20went%20up%20and%20grabbed%20a%20tray%20and%20silverware.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b797d7a3c8094d5dd3910%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222424%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20tray%20read%20%26quot%3BHej!%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHej%26quot%3B%20means%20%26quot%3Bhello%26quot%3B%20in%20Swedish%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0it's%20also%20written%20throughout%20the%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20were%20five%20different%20plates%20of%20cold%20appetizers%20in%20the%20cases.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b7a3e0ec98e92f74fb403%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20were%20a%20variety%20of%20cold%20appetizers.%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20cucumber%20salad%2C%20potato%20salad%2C%20beet%20and%20apple%20salad%2C%20a%20plate%20with%20deviled%20eggs%2C%20cheese%2C%20and%20ham%20on%20it%2C%20gravlax%20(cured%20salmon%20with%20dill)%2C%20and%20pickled%20herring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%20I%20added%20a%20plate%20of%20hot%20food%20to%20my%20tray.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b7af17a3c8094d5dd39e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20is%20where%20I%20found%20the%20famous%20meatballs.%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20some%20meatballs!%20The%20hot%20food%20section%20had%20meatballs%2C%20lingonberry%20jam%2C%20stewed%20red%20cabbage%2C%20ham%2C%20a%20potato%20dish%2C%20mac%20and%20cheese%2C%20and%20salmon.%20I%20told%20an%20employee%20behind%20the%20counter%20what%20I%20wanted%2C%20and%20he%20made%20me%20a%20plate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20grabbed%20some%20kn%C3%A4ckebr%C3%B6d.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b7ba77a3c8094d5dd3a48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20grabbed%20some%20crispbread.%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20tasted%20somewhere%20between%20a%20cracker%20and%20crostini.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%20finally%2C%20I%20sat%20down%20to%20eat.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b7ca750edbc52a86479f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20ended%20up%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20food.%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20final%20tray%2C%20I%20ended%20up%20with%20deviled%20eggs%20(which%20had%20tiny%20shrimp%20on%20them)%2C%20cheese%2C%20cold%20ham%2C%20potato%20salad%2C%20kn%C3%A4ckebr%C3%B6d%2C%20gravlax%2C%20pickled%20herring%2C%20mac%20and%20cheese%2C%20shredded%20potato%20casserole%20red%20cabbage%20with%20apples%2C%20hot%20ham%2C%20and%20finally%2C%20the%20famous%20meatballs%20with%20lingonberry%20jam%20and%20gravy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20shocked%20at%20how%20good%20everything%20tasted.%20Unsurprisingly%2C%20the%20meatballs%20ended%20up%20being%20my%20favorite%2C%20but%20the%20potatoes%20were%20a%20close%20second.%20I%20also%20made%20myself%20an%20open-faced%20sandwich%20of%20gravlax%20and%20cucumber%20salad%20with%20the%20kn%C3%A4ckebr%C3%B6d%2C%20which%20was%20a%20perfect%20vessel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPickled%20herring%20might%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20an%20acquired%20taste%20for%20many%2C%20but%20I'm%20a%20fan%20%E2%80%94%20IKEA's%20tasted%20as%20good%20as%20any%20I've%20had%20in%20the%20past%2C%20sour%2C%20sweet%2C%20and%20not%20too%20fishy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20menu%20is%20determined%20in%20partnership%20with%20our%20partners%20in%20Sweden%2C%26quot%3B%20IKEA%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20the%20event%20to%20feel%20familiar%20and%20true%20to%20the%20traditions%20that%20our%20Swedish%20customers%20and%20co-workers%20might%20be%20missing%2C%20but%20we%20also%20want%20it%20to%20be%20approachable%20to%20customers%20that%20are%20unfamiliar%20with%20Swedish%20cuisine.%20It%20has%20evolved%20slightly%20over%20the%20years.%20We%20now%20incorporate%20more%20plant-based%20options%2C%20for%20example.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20table%20had%20a%20view.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b7ef150edbc52a8648097%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20could%20see%20the%20Manhattan%20skyline%20from%20where%20I%20sat.%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20see%20part%20of%20the%20Manhattan%20skyline%20from%20where%20I%20sat%20to%20eat%2C%20along%20with%20a%20parking%20lot%20full%20of%20school%20busses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%20it%20was%20time%20for%20dessert.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b7f390ec98e92f74fbe87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDessert%20was%20self-serve%20at%20a%20long%20table.%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20different%20desserts%20were%20set%20up%20buffet-style%20on%20a%20long%20table%2C%20some%20with%20little%20signs%20explaining%20what%20they%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20grabbed%20a%20cup%20of%20gl%C3%B6gg.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b7fb350edbc52a8648232%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20were%20bottles%20of%20this%20holiday%20drink%20near%20the%20desserts.%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20tasted%20a%20bit%20similar%20to%20mulled%20wine%2C%20minus%20the%20alcohol.%20It%20was%20well-spiced%2C%20and%20not%20too%20sweet.%20It%20was%20also%20available%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ikea.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fp%2Fvintersaga-gloegg-mulled-fruit-drink-90546384%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20tried%20some%20of%20everything.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b810d7a3c8094d5dd4f6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20tried%20some%20of%20every%20dessert.%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20a%20piece%20of%20almond%20cake%20with%20daim%20(a%20type%20of%20Swedish%20chocolate%20bar)%2C%20a%20cake%20with%20apple%20and%20a%20crumble%20on%20top%2C%20heart-shaped%20gingerbread%20cookies%20called%20pepparkakor%2C%20Swedish%20rice%20pudding%2C%20chocolate%20coconut%20balls%2C%20and%20a%20cinnamon-sugar%20scone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20choose%20a%20favorite%2C%20but%20I%20especially%20loved%20the%20almond%20cake%20and%20the%20rice%20pudding%2C%20which%20was%20topped%20with%20cinnamon%20and%20dried%20berries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELater%20on%2C%20I%20saw%20some%20familiar%20items%20in%20the%20store's%20Swedish%20food%20market.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IKEA%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b827d7a3c8094d5dd5391%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20were%20frozen%20meatballs%20that%20customers%20could%20buy%20and%20take%20home.%3Cp%3EKylie%20Kirschner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20gravlax%20and%20pickled%20herring%20in%20the%20refrigerated%20section%2C%20but%20I%20was%20too%20full%20to%20even%20think%20about%20buying%20more%20food%20(even%20to%20bring%20home).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20expectations%20going%20in%20since%20I%20ended%20up%20attending%20on%20a%20whim%2C%20I%20was%20blown%20away%20by%20the%20overall%20experience%20and%20could%20definitely%20see%20myself%20making%20plans%20to%20coming%20back%20next%20year%20just%20for%20Julbord.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcost-of-living-nyc-millionaires-wealth-tax-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20almost%20everything%20feels%20expensive%20and%20overpriced%2C%20%2420%20seemed%20like%20an%20almost%20laughably%20low%20price%20to%20pay%20for%20how%20good%20the%20food%20was%20and%20how%20much%20of%20it%20I%20got.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20more%20than%20just%20the%20food.%20IKEA%20did%20a%20great%20job%20of%20making%20the%20event%20feel%20special%2C%20from%20the%20festive%20decorations%20to%20the%20live%20music.%20I%20also%20feel%20like%20I%20got%20to%20learn%20a%20little%20bit%20about%20Swedish%20culture%2C%20food%2C%20and%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20IKEA%20Julbord%20is%20now%20a%20year%20away%2C%20sadly.%20Until%20then%2C%20I%20guess%20I'll%20just%20have%20come%20back%20to%20try%20the%20regular%20cafeteria%20%E2%80%94%20they%20won't%20have%20the%20whole%20spread%2C%20but%20I%20can%20at%20least%20get%20some%20more%20of%20those%20meatballs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3