%20Pakistani%20troops%20and%20the%20liberation%20of%20Bangladesh.%20In%20a%20fortnight%20of%20fighting%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20army%20opted%20for%20a%20truce%20over%20war%20following%20a%20well-coordinated%20three-pronged%20attack%20by%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20Air%20Force%20and%20Navy%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20Mukti%20Bahani%2C%20a%20guerilla%20force%20raised%20by%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20officially%20began%20on%20December%203%2C%201971%2C%20and%20within%20three%20days%2C%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20established%20air%20superiority%20in%20East%20Pakistan.%20The%20complete%20domination%20of%20skies%20in%20the%20eastern%20theatre%20played%20a%20decisive%20role%20in%20forcing%2093%2C000%20troops%20to%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAerial%20Supremacy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20posted%20a%20series%20of%20threads%20about%20its%20history%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20highlighting%20the%20crucial%20role%20played%20in%20a%20war%20that%20changed%20the%20world%20map.%20Operations%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20forced%20Lt%20General%20AAK%20Niazi-led%20Pakistani%20forces%20to%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2014%2C%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20bombed%20the%20Governor%20House%20in%20Dhaka%20when%20a%20meeting%20was%20ongoing%20in%20the%20building.%20The%20air%20strike%20had%20such%20a%20demoralizing%20effect%20that%20the%20East%20Pakistan%20government%20resigned%20on%20the%20spot.%20This%20was%20the%20last%20straw%20on%20the%20camel's%20back%20and%20Niazi%20chose%20peace%20over%20more%20fighting.%20A%20day%20later%2C%20Lt%20Gen%20Niazi%20reached%20Indian%20Army%20chief%20General%20Sam%20Manekshaw%2C%20seeking%20a%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Manekshaw%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20expect%20you%20to%20issue%20orders%20to%20all%20forces%20under%20your%20command%20in%20Bangladesh%20to%20ceasefire%20immediately%20and%20surrender%20to%20my%20advancing%20forces.%26quot%3B%20Niazi%20had%20no%20other%20option%20and%20December%2016%20was%20set%20as%20the%20day%20of%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20put%20a%20temporary%20halt%20in%20its%20air%20operations%20till%209%3A00%20am%20on%20December%2016%2C%20this%20pause%20on%20operations%20was%20done%20on%20General%20Manekshaw's%20assurance%20to%20Lt%20Gen%20Niazi%20that%20no%20air%20operation%20would%20be%20conducted%20from%205%3A00%20pm%20on%20December%2015.%20When%20barely%20thirty%20minutes%20were%20left%20before%20the%20%26quot%3Bbombing%20pause%26quot%3B%20expired%20Lt%20Gen%20Niazi%20sought%20an%20extension%20till%203%20pm%20and%20said%20he%20was%20going%20ahead%20with%20the%20surrender%20and%20due%20to%20communication%20and%20isolation%20of%20troops%2C%20requested%20the%20truce%20to%20be%20extended%20by%20six%20hours.%20This%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20demoralizing%20effect%20IAF%20operations%20had%20in%20East%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20temporary%20halt%20in%20air%20operations%20till%200900%20hrs%20on%2016%20Dec%2071%20was%20extended%20to%201500%20hrs%20on%20request%20of%20the%20Pak%20Army%20which%20wanted%20time%20to%20inform%20it's%20troops%20%26amp%3B%20arrange%20a%20surrender%20ceremony.%20This%20extension%20meant%20that%20the%20day's%20first%20air%20strike%20had%20to%20be%20recalled.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2F1971War%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%231971War%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FzBy6zvodw4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FzBy6zvodw4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(%40IAF_MCC)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIAF_MCC%2Fstatus%2F1735850580076306746%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%204%3A31%20pm%2C%20the%20instrument%20of%20surrender%20was%20formally%20signed%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20and%20Lt%20Gen%20AAK%20Niazi%20and%20his%2093%2C000%20troops%20surrendered%20to%20India.%20The%20operations%20on%20the%20western%20theatre%2C%20however%2C%20continued%20an%20air%20interdiction%20campaign%20until%20India%20declared%20a%20unilateral%20ceasefire%20on%20December%2017%2C%201971.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20Of%20This!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20surrender%2C%20a%20senior%20IAF%20officer%20asked%20Lt%20Gen%20Niazi%20why%20he%20had%20surrendered%20when%20his%20army%20was%20still%20intact.%20The%20General%20pointed%20at%20the%20pilot's%20wings%20on%20the%20uniform%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20this%2C%20you%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBECAUSE%20OF%20THIS!%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F79i0QLOpzN%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F79i0QLOpzN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(%40IAF_MCC)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIAF_MCC%2Fstatus%2F1736190268540665883%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20Marshal%20HC%20Dewan%2C%20the%20Air%20Officer%20Commander-in-Chief%2C%20Eastern%20Air%20Command%2C%20was%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20air%20campaign%20in%20the%20east%20and%20the%20IAF's%20speedy%20operations%20and%20dominance%20in%20the%20air%20and%20aerial%20supremacy%20in%20the%20east%20forced%20Pakistan%20to%20surrender%2C%20coupled%20with%20Indian%20Navy's%20blockade%20and%20army%20surrounding%20Dhaka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20coordinated%20offensive%20and%20months%20of%20planning%20resulted%20in%20a%20victory.%20In%20just%2013%20days%2C%20the%20war%20ended.%20Soldiers%20on%20both%20sides%20fought%20gallantly%2C%20with%20some%20fierce%20batt