t%20how%20I%20think%20about%20things.%20It%20was%20very%20important%20to%20me.%20I%20felt%20I%20had%20an%20obligation%20to%20all%20the%20stakeholders%20at%20Amazon%20to%20do%20that.%20And%20so%20having%20turned%20the%20CEO%2C%20I'm%20still%20the%20executive%20chair%20there%2C%20but%20I%20turned%20the%20CEO%20role%20over%2C%20and%20the%20primary%20reason%20I%20did%20that%20is%20that%20I%20could%20spend%20time%20on%20Blue%20Origin%2C%20adding%20some%20energy%2C%20some%20sense%20of%20urgency%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20move%20much%20faster%20and%20we're%20going%20to.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20work%20he%20is%20doing%20at%20Blue%20Origin%2C%20which%20he%20founded%20in%202000%2C%20Jeff%20Bezos%20told%20Mr%20Fridman%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20working%20so%20hard%2C%20and%20I'm%20mostly%20enjoying%20it%2C%20but%20there%20are%20also%20some%20very%20painful%20days.%20Most%20of%20my%20time%20is%20spent%20on%20Blue%20Origin%20and%20I'm%20so%20deeply%20involved%20here%20now%20for%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years.%20And%20in%20the%20big%2C%20I%20love%20it%2C%20and%20the%20small%2C%20there's%20all%20the%20frustrations%20that%20come%20along%20with%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlue%20Origin%20is%20best%20known%20for%20the%20development%20of%20three%20space%20vehicles%2C%20New%20Shepard%2C%20New%20Glenn%2C%20and%20Blue%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702800360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fri0hq7i_jeff-bezos_650x400_04_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjeff-bezos-blue-origin-amazon-jeff-bezos-reveals-why-he-stepped-down-as-amazon-ceo-4689705%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jeff%20Bezos%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20e-commerce%20giant%20Amazon%2C%20has%20shared%20the%20reason%20behind%20his%20decision%20to%20step%20down%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20company%20two%20years%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%