e%20reached%20there%2C%20she%20saw%20him%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20this%20led%20to%20an%20argument.%20She%20alleged%20that%20when%20she%20reached%20into%20Ashwajit's%20car%20to%20collect%20her%20belongings%2C%20he%20asked%20his%20driver%20to%20run%20her%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20fell%20down%20in%20the%20impact%20and%20suffered%20serious%20injuries%2C%20police%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20has%20put%20out%20several%20posts%20on%20social%20media%20over%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20really%20terrified.%20I'm%20very%20scared%20for%20my%20family%20and%20myself.%20I%20don't%20feel%20safe.%20I%20have%20lost%20all%20faith%20in%20humanity.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20my%20life%20is%20ever%20going%20to%20be%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20one%20of%20her%20Instagram%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702799280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Foiqeasg8_priya-singh-ashwajit-gaikwad_625x300_16_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-horror-special-team-to-probe-womans-case-after-being-run-over-by-bureaucrats-son-4689914%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20has%20been%20formed%20to%20probe%20the%20charges%20of%20a%20woman%20that%20her%20boyfriend%20-%20a%20senior%20bureaucrat's%20son%20-%20allegedly%20knocked%20her%20down%20with%20his%20car%20after%20a%20fight%20in%20Thane%20city%20near%20Mumbai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-horror-special-team-to-probe-womans-case-after-being-run-over-by-bureaucrats-son-4689914%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-horror-special-team-to-probe-womans-case-after-being-run-over-by-bureaucrats-son-4689914%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-horror-special-team-to-probe-womans-case