%20inflating%20its%20revenue%2C%20suggesting%20that%20SenseTime%20engaged%20in%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20questionable%20revenue%20round-tripping%20schemes%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20the%20company%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20provided%20funds%20to%20customers%20that%20were%20used%20to%20purchase%20goods%20from%20SenseTime%20that%20may%20not%20have%20ever%20been%20delivered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20SenseTime's%20core%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacial-recognition-company-pimeyes-sued-under-illinois-privacy-law-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efacial%20recognition%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20notoriously%20unprofitable%20due%20to%20intense%20competition%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Chinese%20government%20simply%20does%20not%20make%20a%20practice%20of%20awarding%20highly%20profitable%20contracts%20to%20majority%20foreign-owned%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20Grizzly%20Research%20said%20in%20its%20report%20released%20in%20late%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20company%20argued%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-sensetime.todayir.com%2F20231128124002367210981456_en.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiling%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Hong%20Kong%20Stock%20Exchange%20that%20the%20report%20was%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20merit%20and%20contains%20unfounded%20allegations%20and%20misleading%20conclusions%20and%20interpretations%2C%26quot%3B%20SenseTime's%20stock%20was%20nonetheless%20deeply%20impacted%20by%20the%20accusations%2C%20falling%20nearly%2010%25%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20news%2C%20bringing%20its%20total%20losses%20to%20more%20than%2040%25%20so%20far%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20more%20than%2080%25%20since%20its%20IPO%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fywang%2F2023%2F12%2F16%2Fhong-kong-billionaire-professor-tang-xiaoou-cofounder-of-ai-giant-sensetime-dies-at-55%2F%3Fsh%3D5d35493