lution%20with%20collective%20spirit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20two%20persons%20jumped%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20from%20the%20visitors'%20gallery%20and%20sprayed%20yellow%20colour%20smoke%20when%20the%20Zero%20Hour%20proceedings%20were%20going%20on.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BVery%20Serious%2C%20We%20Need%20To%20Know%20Who's%20Behind%20This%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20On%20Parliament%20Breach%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20remarks%20on%20the%20Parliament%20security%20breach%20last%20week%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20the%20incident%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20need%20to%20debate%26quot%3B%20this%20and%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bdetailed%20investigation%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20carried%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20seriousness%20of%20this%20incident%20should%20not%20be%20downplayed.%20The%20(Lok%20Sabha)%20Speaker%20is%20taking%20all%20the%20necessary%20steps.%20Probe%20agencies%20are%20investigating%20the%20matter.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20find%20out%20which%20elements%20are%20behind%20this%20and%20what%20their%20objectives%20are.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20debate%20this%2C%20there%20should%20be%20a%20detailed%20investigation%20into%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jagran.com%2Fnews%2Fnational-pm-modi-speaks-with-dainik-jagran-on-lok-sabha-security-breach-23606468.html%5C%22%3EDainik%20Jagran%20newspaper%20in%20an%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShocking%20scenes%20played%20out%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20Wednesday%20when%20two%20intruders%20jumped%20from%20desk%20to%20desk%20and%20deployed%20coloured%20smoke%20from%20canisters.%20Their%20co-accused%20staged%20a%20similar%20pr