ing%20employment%20due%20to%20the%20policies%20of%20Modi%20ji%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20hit%20back%2C%20saying%20Mr%20Gandhi%20%26quot%3Balways%20talks%20trash%26quot%3B%20and%20pointing%20out%20that%20unemployment%20was%20at%20its%20lowest%20in%20the%20last%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20I.N.D.I%20Alliance%20leaders%20must%20explain%20the%20close%20linkages%20of%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20Parliament%20breach%20with%20Congress%2C%20TMC%2C%20and%20CPI(M)%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20IT%20in-charge%20Amit%20Malviya%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702797000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fs80nrod8_pm-parliament-ani_625x300_17_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-parliament-security-breach-probe-needed-not-debate-pms-1st-remarks-on-parliament-security-breach-4689780%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20first%20remarks%20on%20the%20Parliament%20security%20breach%20last%20week%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20the%20incident%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20need%20to%20debate%26quot%3B%20this%20and%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bdetailed%20investigation%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20carried%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-parliament-security-breach-probe-needed-not-debate-pms-1st-remarks-on-parliament-security-breach-4689780%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-parliament-security-breach-probe-needed-not-debate-pms-1st-remarks-on-parliament-security-breach-4689780%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-parliament-security-breach-probe-needed-not-debate-pms-1st-remark