.%20Even%20the%20group%20ads%20boast%20not%20of%20viewers%20but%20of%20channels%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98market%20share%E2%80%99.%20Systems%20turn%20away%20again%20and%20again%20from%20the%20elephant%20in%20the%20room%3A%20unemployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20we%20are%20sold%20old%20wine%20in%20new%20bottles%20and%20mutton%20parading%20as%20lamb%2C%20talking%20about%20India%20as%20a%20young%20nation%2C%20youthful%20dreams%2C%20and%20restoring%20the%20lost%20glory%20of%20the%20wonder%20that%20was%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20nation%20hastily%20bulldozes%20these%20angry%20young%20voices%2C%20it%20must%20take%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20face%20the%20real-time%20issues%20that%20will%20remain%20unresolved%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20margin%20political%20parties%20may%20win.%20The%20basic%20flaw%20must%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20get%20buried%20under%20ritual%20and%20spectacle.%20In%20this%20instance%2C%20it%20lies%20in%20a%20poor%20security%20set%20up%20for%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building.%20The%20building%20was%20inaugurated%20not%20too%20long%20ago%20in%20a%20ritualistic%20ceremony%2C%20with%20a%20horde%20of%20portly%20Sadhus%20carrying%20a%20gold%20mace%2C%20The%20Holy%20Sengol%20%E2%80%93%20an%20ancient%20symbol%20of%20divine%20authority%20%E2%80%93%20and%20planting%20it%20in%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20of%20Democracy%20amid%20Vedic%20chants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20media%20buzz%20was%20good%20Vastu%2C%20holy%20Mantras%20and%20ancient%20rituals%20that%20protect%20our%20culture%20and%20democracy.%20There%20was%20not%20a%20whiff%20of%20the%20objective%20conditions%20many%20of%20our%20youngsters%20are%20growing%20in.%20Some%20will%20view%20this%20question%20as%20cynical.%20After%20all%2C%20they%20ask%2C%20such%20conditions%20exist%20in%20many%20countries%2C%20but%20a%20blatant%20attack%20within%20the%20Parliament%20building%20by%20half%20a%20dozen%20rank%20amateurs%20with%20personal%20grievances%20against%20the%20system%2C%20does%20not%20erupt%20there.%20Why%20did%20it%20happen%20here%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy%20so%20suddenly%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-yellow-smoke-signals-tell-us-about-the-mother-of-democracy%5C%22%3EWhat%20Yellow%20Smoke%20Signals%20Tell%20Us%20About%20the%20%E2%80%98Mother%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20sudden%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20reports.%20The%20educated%20but%20jobless%20individuals%20had%20met%20briefly%20in%20Mysuru%20over%20a%20year%20ago.%20Since%20then%2C%20they%20kept%20in%20touch%20on%20Facebook%20and%20recently%20reunited%20in%20Gurugram%2C%20the%20Maximum%20City%20of%20the%20north%2C%20to%20shape%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20draw%20attention%20to%20their%20plight.%20Facebook%20is%20a%20bubble%20created%20for%20their%20kind%20by%20a%20Harvard%20sophomore%20to%20whom%20%E2%80%98connectivity%20among%20the%20young%E2%80%99%20was%20the%20Holy%20Grail.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Fan%20Club%20page%2C%20built%20around%20the%20celebrated%20rebel%20against%20British%20colonialism%20who%20had%20also%20hurled%20a%20dummy%20bomb%20at%20the%20highest%20authority%2C%20became%20the%20catalyst.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENet%20is%20where%20our%20youngsters%20live%2024%C3%977.%20And%20everything%20shrinks%20on%20Facebook%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20mini%20India%20for%20the%20young%2C%20with%20time%20on%20their%20hands%20that%20they%20can%20roam%20freely%20to%20meet%20like-minded%20people.%20Here%20is%20where%20a%20Neelam%20Azad%2C%20the%20jobless%20daughter%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehalwai%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Jind%20who%20has%20an%20M.Ed%20degree%2C%20has%20passed%20the%20NET%2C%20HTET%2C%20CTET%20exams%20and%20still%20failed%20to%20get%20a%20job%2C%20could%20meet%20another%20disgruntled%2026-year-old%20Sagar%20Sharma%2C%20son%20of%20a%20carpenter%2C%20who%20had%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20school%20for%20lack%20of%20money%20and%20drive%20an%20auto%20rickshaw%20in%20Lucknow%20for%20a%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20met%20a%20jobless%20engineer%2C%20Manoranjan%20(34)%20from%20Mysuru%2C%20the%20son%20of%20a%20farmer%20and%20Amol%20Shinde%20(25)%2C%20a%20Dalit%20from%20Latur%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20who%20failed%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20army%20and%20was%20deemed%20too%20old%20for%20becoming%20an%20Agniveer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Facebook%2C%20Vishal%20Sharma%20and%20Lalit%20Jha%20promised%20to%20provide%20board%20and%20lodging%20to%20their%20out%20of%20town%20online%20friends.%20Thus%2C%20a%20Wild%20West%20of%20Facebook%20became%20home%20for%20the%20revolutionary%20fantasies%20of%20lost%2C%20frustrated%2C%20and%20angry%20souls.%20No%20wonder%20there%20is%20a%20haphazard%20and%20accidental%20quality%20to%20their%20attack.%20The%20younger%20ones%2C%20Amol%20and%20Sagar%2C%20entered%20the%20Parliament%2C%20courtesy%20passes%20provided%20by%20the%20staff%20of%20an%20unsuspecting%20MP%2C%20and%20created%20terror%20within%2C%20while%20the%20older%20ones%2C%20Neelam%20and%20Manoranjan%2C%20raised%20slogans%20and%20waved%20spray%20cans%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20bystanders%20were%20petrified%20and%20revolted%2C%20the%20media%20vultures%20entered%2C%20fighting%20over%20a%20can%20of%20tear%20gas.%20Rich%20Black%20humour%20there%2C%20but%20also%20so%20much%20unspoken%20pain!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20evening%2C%20the%20general%20reaction%20had%20subsided%20as%20authorities%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98Godi%E2%80%99%20media%20went%20into%20overdrive%20trying%20to%20find%20links%20with%20all%20deemed%20subversives%3A%20Maoists%2C%20Naxals%2C%20and%20the%20Opposition%20looking%20to%20draw%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20moment%20when%20a%20nascent%20movement%20limited%20to%20some%20half%20a%20dozen%20men%20and%20women%20butted%20headlong%20in%20a%20structure%20they%20felt%20no%20longer%20cared%20for%20them.%20Like%20children%20throwing%20tantrums%2C%20they%20tried%20to%20destroy%20and%20de%20sanctify%20whatever%20they%20could%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20their%20anger%3A%20chairs%2C%20tables%2C%20papers%2C%20files%2C%20a%20mic%20here%20and%20a%20bag%20there.%20But%20these%20acts%20were%20impulsive%20and%20short-lived%2C%20a%20poor%20theatre%2C%20if%20you%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20condemnable%20but%20puny%20revolt%20underscores%20anything%2C%20it%20is%20this%3A%20sometimes%20money%20and%20spectacles%20are%20not%20enough%20to%20sustain%20the%20grand%20illusion%3B%20hollow%20promises%20are%20no%20longer%20working.%20There%20is%20an%20Iranian%20proverb%20that%20says%3A%20Promises%20have%20value%20only%20for%20those%20that%20believe%20in%20them.%20The%20Parliament%20security%20breach%20incident%20on%20December%2013%20showed%20us%20a%20rare%20glimpse%20of%20what%20many%20did%20not%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20play%20gone%20bad%20could%2C%20if%20immediate%20remedial%20action%20is%20not%20taken%2C%20become%20a%20violent%20rapacious%20spectacle%20where%20characters%20will%20again%20invade%20the%20stage%20suddenly%2C%20looking%20for%20a%20new%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702794200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14095043%2FGBN2cf7bMAANLsZ.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwho-are-our-young-andolanjeevis%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20December%2013%20incident%20showed%20us%20a%20rare%20glimpse%20of%20what%20many%20did%20not%20see.%20What%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20play%20gone%20bad%20could%2C%20if%20immediate%20remedial%20action%20is%20not%20taken%2C%20become%20a%20violent%20rapacious%20spectacle%20where%20characters%20will%20again%20invade%20the%20stage%20suddenly%2C%20looking%20for%20a%20new%20author.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwho-are-our-young-andolanjeevis%22%2C%22cdnAm