20Hindu%20woman%20was%20murdered%20allegedly%20by%20her%20Muslim%20partner%2C%20was%20used%20as%20a%20point%20of%20reference%20to%20amp%20up%20anti-Muslim%20rhetoric.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20Chiplun%20police%20for%20raising%20questions%20over%20the%20provocative%20nature%20of%20the%20sloganeering.%20The%20slogans%20by%20the%20Sanatan%20Sanstha%20went%20without%20notice%20while%20requests%20to%20stop%20vitiating%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20the%20town%20was%20seen%20as%20an%20act%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdisrupting%20public%20harmony%E2%80%9D.%20My%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fusing-love-jihad-as-a-rallying-cry-sanatan-sanstha-attempts-to-communalise-the-konkan%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20same%20incident%20gives%20a%20detailed%20account%20of%20Sanathan%20Sanstha%E2%80%99s%20past.%20An%20organisation%20accused%20of%20murdering%20rationalists%20like%20Narendra%20Dabholkar%20and%20Govind%20Pansare%20was%20not%20getting%20the%20attention%20it%20should%20have%20got%20from%20the%20police.%20But%20the%20story%20didn%E2%80%99t%20end%20there%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20had%20only%20begun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rally%20in%20Chiplun%20was%20actually%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20anti-Muslim%20campaign%20prevalent%20throughout%20the%20state%2C%20and%20organised%20at%20scale.%20This%20campaign%20was%20conducted%20under%20a%20new%20entity%20called%20the%20Sakal%20Hindu%20Samaj%20(SHS).%20SHS%20consisted%20of%20a%20spectrum%20of%20Hindutva%20groups%20like%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%2C%20Sanatan%20Sanstha%2C%20Hindu%20Janjagruti%20Samiti%2C%20Vishwa%20Shriram%20Sena%2C%20Shri%20Ram%20Pratishthan%20Hindustan%20and%20Durga%20Vahini%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20initial%20half%20of%202023%2C%20a%20startling%20revelation%20emerged%3A%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhate-speech-bjp-anti-muslim-2023%5C%22%3Esubstantial%2029%25%20of%20hate%20speeches%20