ion%2C%20Shiv%20Pratishthan%20Hindusthan%20and%20its%20leader%2C%20Manohar%20Kulkarni%2C%20alias%20Sambhaji%20Bhide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhide%20has%20an%20influence%20among%20the%20youth%20in%20Kolhapur%20and%20nearby%20areas.%20His%20affinity%20with%20the%20RSS%20is%20an%20open%20secret.%20Boys%20from%20Shiv%20Pratishthan%20Hindusthan%20were%20accused%20of%20fanning%20the%20riots%20in%20Kolhapur.%20We%20investigate%20this%20case%20and%20shed%20more%20light%20on%20his%20politics%20and%20influence%2C%20by%20talking%20to%20former%20associates%20of%20Bhide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20third%20and%20concluding%20part%20of%20the%20series%20also%20delves%20on%20the%20role%20Marathi%20literature%20and%20films%20have%20had%20in%20developing%20and%20fomenting%20an%20anti-Muslim%20narrative.%20The%20docuseries%20goes%20on%20to%20discuss%20Shiv%20Sena-(Uddhav%20Thackeray)%E2%80%99s%20influence%20in%20the%20state%20and%20poses%20the%20question%2C%20if%20its%20newly%20found%20positioning%20in%20INDIA%2C%20as%20an%20anti-BJP%20force%2C%20be%20a%20catalyst%20for%20change%20and%20for%20the%20better%20in%20Maharashtra%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FfuYtfdmUltk%3Fsi%3DGF7Tub494yWoqHyM%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702789256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17101550%2FTHUMBNAIL.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnaf-rath-in-maharashtra-end-of-reason%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20three-part%20special%20documentary%20series%20on%20the%20spread%20of%20communal%20division%20and%20hate%20in%20Maharashtra.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnaf-rath-in-maharashtra-end-of-reason%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20Oman%20Discuss%20Gaza%20Conflict%2C%20Back%20Two-State%20Solution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20discussed%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%20and%20affirmed%20the%20need%20to%20achieve%20a%20two-state%20solution%20with%20the%20visiting%20Omani%20sultan%2C%20Haitham%20bin%20Tariq%2C%20who%20is%20the%20first%20Arab%20leader%20to%20visit%20India%20since%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20region%20over%20two%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sultan%20is%20the%20first%20Omani%20head%20of%20state%20to%20visit%20India%20in%2026%20years.%20He%20took%20over%20in%202020%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Sultan%20Qaboos%20bin%20Said%20Al%20Said%2C%20who%20had%20last%20visited%20Delhi%20in%201997.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20having%20arrived%20a%20day%20earlier%2C%20the%20sultan%20of%20Oman%20held%20formal%20talks%20with%20his%20host%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20media%20briefing%20after%20the%20discussions%2C%20foreign%20secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cgiven%20the%20developments%20in%20West%20Asia%20in%20terms%20of%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20there%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20multiple%20challenges%20that%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%20has%20thrown%20up%2C%20that%20was%20definitely%20an%20important%20element%20of%20discussions%20between%20the%20two%20leaders%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cshared%20appreciation%20of%20the%20continuing%20challenge%20that%20both%20countries%20face%20from%20the%20emerging%20multiple%20dimensions%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20including%20the%20catastrophic%20humanitarian%20situation%2C%20which%20is%20there%2C%20the%20challenge%20of%20terrorism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foreign%20secretary%20also%20asserted%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20were%20committed%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20need%20to%20find%20and%20try%20and%20achieve%20a%20two-state%20solution%20as%20a%20way%20forward%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOman%2C%20which%20is%20known%20to%20have%20a%20moderate%2C%20balancing%20position%20in%20the%20Gulf%2C%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.muscatdaily.com%2F2023%2F10%2F07%2Foman-calls-on-palestine-israel-to-exercise-restraint%2F%5C%22%3Einitially%20called%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20both%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20to%20exercise%20restraint%20after%20the%20Hamas%20terror%20attack%20of%20October%207.%20Following%20the%20heavy%20toll%20after%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20counter-strikes%20hit%20Gaza%20strip%2C%20Oman%20has%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Finternational%2520community%2520to%2520conduct%2520an%2520impartial%2520investigation%2520into%2520Israeli%2520actions%2520in%2520the%2520Gaza%2520Strip%5C%22%3Einternational%20probe%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20Israeli%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20unequivocally%20denounced%20terrorism%20in%20all%20its%20manifestations%20and%20agreed%20that%20no%20act%20of%20terror%20could%20be%20justified%20under%20any%20circumstances%2C%20as%20mentioned%20in%20the%20joint%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20naming%20any%20country%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F37458%2FTranscript_of_Special_Briefing_by_Foreign_Secretary_on_the_State_Visit_of_Sultan_of_Oman_to_India_December_16_2023%5C%22%3Ethe%20joint%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20underlined%20the%20%E2%80%9Cneed%20for%20all%20countries%20to%20abide%20by%20international%20law%2C%20respect%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20all%20nations%2C%20refrain%20from%20interfering%20in%20the%20internal%20affairs%20of%20other%20countries%2C%20an