ll%20the%20working%20women%20in%20India%3A%20Learn%20to%20live%20with%20sexual%20harassment.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20truth%20of%20our%20lives.%20The%20POSH%20ACT%20is%20a%20big%20wholesome%20lie%20told%20to%20us.%20No%20one%20listens%2C%20no%20one%20bothers%E2%80%A6.And%20I%20am%20judge.%20I%20could%20not%20even%20a%20muster%20a%20fair%20enquiry%20for%20myself%2C%20let%20alone%20justice.%20I%20advise%20all%20women%20to%20learn%20to%20be%20a%20toy%2C%20or%20a%20non-living%20thing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702724067000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fcivil-judges-letter-cji-sexual-harassment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20POSH%20ACT%20is%20a%20big%20wholesome%20lie%20told%20to%20us.%20No%20one%20listens%2C%20no%20one%20bothers...And%20I%20am%20judge.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fcivil-judges-letter-cji-sexual-harassment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kuwaiti%20leader%20Sheikh%20Nawaf%20al-Ahmed%20dies%20aged%2086%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702721619000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F83B3%2Fproduction%2F_115651733_breaking-large-promo-nc.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67736721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sheikh%20Emir%20Nawaf%20al-Ahmad%20al-Jaber%20al-Sabah%20had%20led%20the%20country%20for%20the%20last%20three%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A102%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67736721%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67736721.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67736721.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paul%20Lynch%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Prophet%20S