F%2Ftime.com%2F6255425%2Findia-raid-bbc-modi-documentary%2F%5C%22%3Eharassed%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20tax%20raids%20in%20February%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Justice%20Nariman%20highlighted%20the%20role%20of%20courts%20in%20stemming%20the%20infringement%20of%20the%20media%E2%80%99s%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20moment%20there%20is%20any%20onslaught%20on%20the%20media%2C%20the%20courts%20must%20be%20vigilant%20to%20instantly%20scotch%20it.%20If%20you%20find%20that%20there%20is%20some%20independent%20reporting%20which%20has%20led%20to%20something%20as%20a%20result%20of%20which%20there%20is%20a%20tax%20raid%20then%20for%20that%20reason%20alone%20you%20must%20say%20that%20the%20tax%20raid%20is%20illegal%20and%20unconstitutional%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20if%20%E2%80%9Cour%20watchdog%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20media%20%E2%80%93%20is%20killed%2C%20then%20nothing%20remains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Findia-slips-in-world-press-freedom-index-ranks-161-out-of-180-countries%2Farticle66806608.ece%5C%22%3Egovernment%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20attacks%20on%20media%20freedom%20and%20democracy%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20illustrated%20by%20raids%20and%20arrests%20of%20prominent%20journalists.%20India%20ranks%20161%20out%20of%20180%20countries%20on%20the%20Press%20Freedom%20Index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Nariman%20also%20had%20heavy%20words%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frajya-sabha-passes-bill-election-commissioners-opposition-appointment%5C%22%3EElection%20Commission%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20introduced%20in%20the%20parliament%20and%20since%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ordered%20that%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20the%20ECs%20should%20be%20selected%20by%20a%20panel%20comprising%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20O